Frame_Modulo: apply motion diffusion every n-th frame

preprocessing noise filtering {1: median filtering only before diffusion stage, 2: median filtering and BM3D before diffusion and levelset stages, 3: BM3D only before diffusion and levelset stages, 4: autoencoder before diffusion and levelset stages}
number of tiles per dimension in CLAHE
probability threshold for clipping
spatio-temporal diffusion type index (integer). Options: {1: 'linear', 2: 'non-linear'}
temporal step of ST diffusion PDE
temporal to spatial lambda ratio of ST diffusion PDE
iteration number of ST diffusion PDE
diffusivity parameter of ST diffusion PDE

watershed segmentation input index (integer). Options: {1:'diff_frame_and_edge_min',2:'diff_frame_and_feat_map_max',3:'diff_frame_and_edge_min_and_feat_map_max',4:'feat_map_and_edge_min',4:'feat_map_and_feat_map_max',6:'feat_map_and_edge_min_and_feat_map_max'}
std dev of Gaussian kernel for density estimation (edge map)
h-minima value for reconstruction before watershed on intensity map
reference percentile for F/B separation
level set type identifier. Options: {1:'chan_vese',2:'lse_bfe'}
max iteration number of C-V segmentation
contour length regularization parameter for C-V segmentation (greater values imply greater weight of contour curvature in level set evolution)
h-minima value for reconstruction before cell separation on SDT

motion activity criterion index (integer).  Options: {1:'original',2:'diffused',3:'st_gradient',4:'regions_diffused',5:'regions_st_gradient',6:'regions_active_pixels',7:'regions_st_laplace',8:'regions_st_moments',9:'regions_st_hessian',10:'regions_sp_hessian_tempo_deriv'}
foreground/background detection index (integer). Options: {1:'cdf_mam',2:'cdf_joint',3:'normal_pdf_joint',4:'kde_pdf_joint',5:'classifier'}
standard deviation value for foreground/background separation
